http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/Bereaved-family-members-stage-dharna/article13980011.ece

The family members of Komirelly Venkat Reddy (70), who was killed in an accident near Narketpally on Saturday, staged a protest on NH-65 here on Sunday, demanding compensaion.The driver of the car attempted to speed away from the spot with the body of Venkat Reddy caught on the top of the car.The kin demanded that the State government construct a bridge across the NH-65 at Kamineni Hospital to provide safe passage to locals.The officials assured the family members that they would take up the issue with higher-ups.